item.title: School Projects
item.description: Here are some school projects that I have worked on. Project 1: Photoshop This project was done in my Electronic Art class. I utilized photoshop to create a visualization of ways to communicate with animals. Project 2: Emoji This project was also done in Electronic Art. I created a new emoji that I think could be useful.
